TEXT -1448 -336 Left 2 !.tran 0 2m 800u 20n uic
TEXT 496 -1080 Left 2 !.param Pout=500\n.param Vout=48\n.param Vin=390\n.param RL={Vout**2/Pout}\n.param DT=50n ; deadtime for the MOSFETs\n*\n.param Gfc=-8.8 ; magnitude at crossover *\n.param PS=-89 ; phase lag at crossover *\n*\n* Enter Design Goals Information Here *\n*\n.param fc=10k ; targeted crossover *\n.param PM=70 ; choose phase margin at crossover *\n*\n*\n* Enter the Values for Vout and Bridge Bias Current *\n*\n.param Ibias=1m\n.param Vref=2.5\n.param Rpullup=18k ; this is the internal FB resistance\n*\n* Enter opto characteristics *\n*\n.param Fopto=100k\n.param Copto={1/(2*pi*Fopto*Rpullup)}\n.param CTR=0.35\n*\n.param Vaux=5\n.param VL=2.5\n.param VCEsat=0.3\n.param Vdd=5\n.param Ib=1m\n.param Vf=1\n.param A={Vaux-Vf-VL}\n.param B={Vdd-VCEsat+Ib*CTR*Rpullup}\n.param Rmax={(A/B)*Rpullup*CTR}\n.param RLED={0.8*Rmax}\n*\n* Do not edit the below lines *\n*\n.param Rlower={Vref/Ibias}\n.param Rupper={(Vout-Vref)/Ibias}\n.param boost={PM-PS-90}\n.param kf={tan((boost/2+45)*pi/180)}\n.param G1={Rpullup*CTR/RLED}\n.param G2={10**(-Gfc/20)}\n.param G={G2/G1}\n.param fp={fc*kf}\n.param fz={fc/kf}\n.param d={(fz**2+fc**2)*(fp**2+fc**2)}\n.param c={(fz**2+fc**2)}\n.param R2={(sqrt(d)/c)*G*fc*Rupper/fp}\n.param C1={1/(2*pi*fz*R2)}\n.param C2={1/(2*pi*fp*Rpullup)}\n.param Ccol={C2-Copto}\n*
TEXT 624 960 Left 2 ;The dc labels are the values of the components:\npV --> pF\nnV --> nF\nkV --> kOhms
TEXT -1448 -296 Left 2 !.MODEL TOFSW2 SW(Ron=10m Roff=100Meg Vt=2 Vh=1)\n.MODEL DTOF D(IS=10e-18 RS=16m CJO=50p N=100m)
TEXT -1440 -144 Left 2 !.options abstol=1u vntol=1m reltol=0.01 gmin=100p\n+method=gear
